CANON INFORMATION
From Official Spoiler Document:

"Franco-Belgian comic lover"

This is the ONLY canon descriptor for Roos.
What This Tells Us:

She loves Franco-Belgian comics (bandes dessinées) - the comic genre from France/Belgium
Comics like Tintin, Asterix, Spirou, Lucky Luke, etc.
This defines her character - she's the comics nerd

Important Note: The official document says she loves Franco-Belgian comics, NOT that she IS French/Belgian. Her origin is unconfirmed canon.

