TL;DR:
Roos is the "Franco-Belgian comic lover" - her only official descriptor. She's nerdy but socially successful, with brown hair in side ponytail, green eyes, and perpetual sunny smile wearing yellow/orange clothes. Loves comics like Tintin, Asterix, Spirou. Likely draws comics herself inspired by ligne claire style. Best friends with Ilse in creative partnership: Roos draws, Ilse writes, they create comics together. Confident in her interests despite being nerdy. Perpetual smiler like Coco. Bridge between social groups. Makes wholesome adventure comics with Ilse. Dreams of publishing their work someday.
